dc_title_s: Map of a portion of Atlantic City
dc_description_s: Map of a portion of Atlantic City, NJ showing Dr. Charles B. Penrose acreage within bounds of proposed harbor improvement, exclusive of waterways (owned by State of NJ) and lots on north side of Clam Creek, and 150 foot average depth on west side of Beach Thoroughfare. Map depicts North and South Fork of Clam Creek.
